<P>
Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA022694-0040 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 017352 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 26, 1994, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 4; Column 5; Metro Desk 
</P>
