<DOCNO> LA022694-0169 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 017481 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 26, 1994, Saturday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Home Design; Part N; Page 2; Column 5; View Desk 
</P>
