<TEXT>
<P>
 Coach: Don Turnbull (first year). 
</P>
<P>
 1992-93: Empire League runner-up. 
</P>
<P>
 Key returners: Jeremy Becker, Sr., LJ, TJ; Greg Cleave, Jr., 100, 200; Jimmy 
Hutsell, Sr., 200, 400; Jason Sandoval, Jr., 800, 1600, 3200. 
</P>
<P>
 Key newcomers: Wes Bunn Jr., Fr., LJ; Adolfo Cruz, Fr., 1,600-3,200. 
</P>
