Empire League quarter mile (49.29) and was fourth (49.06) in the Southern 
Section Division II finals. Cleave finished as the league champion at 200 
meters (22.22) and was second at 100 meters. Becker is an all-around jumper 
(45-11 in the triple jump and 21-4 1/2 in the long jump) who might dabble in 
the high hurdles. Cruz, a miler in the low 4:30s as an eighth grader, will 
split time with the Cypress baseball team, and Bunn has enough athletic talent 
to start on the varsity basketball team as a freshman. 
